42
00:03:38.339 --> 00:03:40.500
asset window.

43
00:03:40.500 --> 00:03:45.360
Instead of manually fitting a metahuman preset to your scanner sculpt, you can simply use

44
00:03:45.360 --> 00:03:51.159
the standard MESH to metahuman workflow to generate an initial metahuman identity.

45
00:03:51.159 --> 00:03:56.360
The benefits of this is that you can align the metahuman identity with the headscan,

46
00:03:56.360 --> 00:04:02.039
making it easier to transfer textures from the scanned data to the identity.

47
00:04:02.039 --> 00:04:07.479
To get started, you will first create an initial metahuman identity by importing and preparing

48
00:04:07.479 --> 00:04:08.960
the mesh.

49
00:04:08.960 --> 00:04:14.379
Since this is an image-based solve, using a texture can help to track the facial features

50
00:04:14.379 --> 00:04:15.379
better.

51
00:04:15.379 --> 00:04:20.900
Next, create a metahuman identity asset and populate it.

52
00:04:20.900 --> 00:04:25.540
Create and track a neutral pose and run the identity solve.

53
00:04:25.540 --> 00:04:31.460
From there, you can enable and adjust additional trackers and spend a good amount of time on

54
00:04:31.460 --> 00:04:35.579
the eyes and mouth to get a more precise solve.

55
00:04:35.579 --> 00:04:43.899
Once you are finished, submit the template mesh to the metahuman backend.

56
00:04:43.899 --> 00:04:50.159
To export the metahuman identity conformed mesh from the metahuman identity asset, in

57
00:04:50.159 --> 00:04:57.560
the command prompt, enter, mh, identity, export meshes, and the number 1.

58
00:04:57.560 --> 00:05:03.199
Once you hit enter, in the main toolbar, select metahuman identity solve.

59
00:05:03.659 --> 00:05:08.740
Next, locate the conformed mesh.

60
00:05:08.740 --> 00:05:15.079
To locate the conformed mesh, go to the File Explorer folder of the Unreal Engine project.

61
00:05:15.079 --> 00:05:20.539
In the saved folder, the obj file of the mesh that was used for the solve will include the

62
00:05:20.539 --> 00:05:22.919
name ScannedMesh.

63
00:05:22.919 --> 00:05:28.419
In the folder with the name of the metahuman identity asset, the obj file that includes

64
00:05:28.420 --> 00:05:35.420
the name conformal face mesh will be the conformed mesh of the metahuman identity and it will

65
00:05:35.420 --> 00:05:37.879
be of metahuman topology.

66
00:05:37.879 --> 00:05:42.860
The next step of this workflow is to bring these meshes into your choice of 3D software

67
00:05:42.860 --> 00:05:44.860
to inspect them.

68
00:05:44.860 --> 00:05:50.980
And from there, you can refit any details that were lost during the solve back onto the conformed

69
00:05:50.980 --> 00:05:52.300
mesh.

70
